{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AhUXLPDpZoBa2keVhGvvew","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So in iteration 19, SAFFRON was passing and Smażona was failing. In iteration 20, SAFFRON is failing and Smażona is passing. This is a swap — the fix for Smażona broke SAFFRON.\n\nNow let me figure out what changed between iteration 19 and iteration 20 that caused SAFFRON to break. The iteration 19 feedback (which I read) described the `commonShort2` expansion as the cause of Smażona's failure, and suggested adding Polish cooking verbs to `looksLikeCookingInstruction` as a fix. So the fix in the code from iter 19 → iter 20 likely extended `looksLikeCookingInstruction` to include Polish verbs.\n\n\nLet me check the current code to see which Polish cooking verbs were added and trace through how they'd affect the SAFFRON file.\n\nExamining the regex pattern...\n\nStill writing verb patterns... I'm tracing through how the SAFFRON file gets processed: \"BUNS\" and \"ssekart\" both fail the cooking instruction check since they're single words, and the garble detection also returns false for \"BUNS\" since it's only 4 characters. The cooking instruction prologue check then starts at line 0, but since the first line doesn't look like a cooking instruction, the loop stops immediately without skipping ahead.\n\nNow I'm puzzled about why SAFFRON passed in iteration 19 but is failing in iteration 20, especially since the changes were supposedly meant to fix a different file. Let me check what actually changed between those two commits to see if something unintended affected this file's handling. The cooking instruction prologue check shouldn't be affecting SAFFRON since its opening lines don't match that pattern. So I need to figure out what else changed between iterations 19 and 20 that could break this specific test. Let me compare the actual code differences using git to see what was modified.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":391,"cache_read_input_tokens":58682,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":391},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eb533174-fed4-4e6a-8d51-5fccd85ce376","uuid":"512c9f5b-4850-4fc9-bafc-46182241280d"}
